## Changelog

### v0.2.1 - Enhanced Market Utilities & Time Resolution Support

- ‚úÖ **Smart Period Calculation**: Added `calc_delivery_period()` function with IPEX/OMIE convention support
- ‚úÖ **Long Period Downloads**: Added `download_long_period()` for efficient chunked data retrieval
- ‚úÖ **Enhanced Time Resolution**: Added time_resolution field to response models (PT60M/PT15M)
- ‚úÖ **Imbalance Data Improvements**: Separate endpoints for 15-minute and 60-minute historical data
- ‚úÖ **DST Handling**: Automatic Daylight Saving Time handling in period calculations
- ‚úÖ **Enhanced Response Models**: Updated models with comprehensive time resolution support

