- ‚úÖ **Enhanced Security**: JWT token validation and secure session management
- ‚úÖ **New Clients**: Added specialized clients for generation, load, flows, and imbalance data
- ‚úÖ **Improved Error Handling**: Comprehensive exception hierarchy with detailed error information
- ‚úÖ **Better Type Safety**: Enhanced enum validation and parameter checking
- ‚úÖ **Advanced Logging**: Structured logging with credential protection
- ‚úÖ **Configuration Management**: Secure configuration loading from environment and files
- ‚úÖ **Timezone Utilities**: Enhanced timezone handling for European energy markets
- ‚úÖ **Response Models**: Detailed response models for all data types
- ‚úÖ **Optional Dependencies**: Flexible installation with optional features

